  53,19,"afraytm- 'ayuha almshrkwn- hadhih alalihat alty tebdwnha: allaat walezza wamanat althaalithat alakhra, hal nafaeat 'aw drrat hataa takun shuraka' llh?"
  53,20,"afraytm- 'ayuha almshrkwn- hadhih alalihat alty tebdwnha: allaat walezza wamanat althaalithat alakhra, hal nafaeat 'aw drrat hataa takun shuraka' llh?"
  53,21,"atjelwn lakum aldhdhakr aldhy trdwnh, watajealun lilah bzemkm alantha alty la tardawnaha lanfskm? tilk 'idhana qismat jayr. ma hadhih al'awthan 'iilaa 'asma'an lays laha min awsaf alkmal shy', 'iinama hi 'asma'an samaytumuha 'antum wabawukum bmqtda ahwaykm albatlt, ma 'anzal allah biha min hujat tasadaq dewakm fyha. ma yatabie hwla' almushrikun 'iilaa alzn, whwa 'anfusahum almnhrft ean alftrt alslymt, walaqad ja'ahum min rabihim ealaa lisan alnabiu salaa allah ealayh wslm, ma fih hdaythm, fama antfeu bh"
  53,22,"atjelwn lakum aldhdhakr aldhy trdwnh, watajealun lilah bzemkm alantha alty la tardawnaha lanfskm? tilk 'idhana qismat jayr. ma hadhih al'awthan 'iilaa 'asma'an lays laha min awsaf alkmal shy', 'iinama hi 'asma'an samaytumuha 'antum wabawukum bmqtda ahwaykm albatlt, ma 'anzal allah biha min hujat tasadaq dewakm fyha. ma yatabie hwla' almushrikun 'iilaa alzn, whwa 'anfusahum almnhrft ean alftrt alslymt, walaqad ja'ahum min rabihim ealaa lisan alnabiu salaa allah ealayh wslm, ma fih hdaythm, fama antfeu bh"
  53,23,"atjelwn lakum aldhdhakr aldhy trdwnh, watajealun lilah bzemkm alantha alty la tardawnaha lanfskm? tilk 'idhana qismat jayr. ma hadhih al'awthan 'iilaa 'asma'an lays laha min awsaf alkmal shy', 'iinama hi 'asma'an samaytumuha 'antum wabawukum bmqtda ahwaykm albatlt, ma 'anzal allah biha min hujat tasadaq dewakm fyha. ma yatabie hwla' almushrikun 'iilaa alzn, whwa 'anfusahum almnhrft ean alftrt alslymt, walaqad ja'ahum min rabihim ealaa lisan alnabiu salaa allah ealayh wslm, ma fih hdaythm, fama antfeu bh"
  53,24,"lys lil'iinsan ma tmnah min shafaeat hadhih almebwdat 'aw ghyrha mimaa thwah nfsh, falilah 'amr aldunya walakhrt"
  53,25,"lys lil'iinsan ma tmnah min shafaeat hadhih almebwdat 'aw ghyrha mimaa thwah nfsh, falilah 'amr aldunya walakhrt"